The way you guys think,it's much more logical.

1137
01:08:24,220 --> 01:08:25,540
Much more analytical.
更具分析性。

1138
01:08:25,800 --> 01:08:27,540
You guys are asking great questions, okay?
你们提出了很好的问题，行吗？

1139
01:08:27,740 --> 01:08:29,120
So, um...
嗯……

1140
01:08:29,120 --> 01:08:31,500
Thank you again, because...
再次感谢你们，因为……

1141
01:08:31,500 --> 01:08:36,240
You don't have to work hard in this course, but you chose to work hard.
你们在这门课里不必费劲，但你们选择了努力。

1142
01:08:36,460 --> 01:08:40,270
And this is gonna carry you very far, um...
这将把你们带得很远，嗯……

1143
01:08:40,860 --> 01:08:42,220
in life, okay?
在生活里，行吗？

1144
01:08:42,520 --> 01:08:44,500
So, um...
所以，嗯……

1145
01:08:44,500 --> 01:08:46,200
The course is...
这门课是……

1146
01:08:47,620 --> 01:08:50,520
Um... Has come to an end.
嗯……已经结束。

1147
01:08:50,880 --> 01:08:53,380
And I will share with you
我会与大家分享

1148
01:08:54,880 --> 01:08:57,340
um... Why I teach this course, okay?
嗯……我为什么开这门课，行吗？

1149
01:08:58,340 --> 01:09:00,880
Because... Some of you know,
因为……你们中有些人知道，

1150
01:09:01,120 --> 01:09:04,760
I do have a very prestigious education background,
我确实拥有非常有名望的教育背景，

1151
01:09:04,900 --> 01:09:07,700
as well as a career background,
以及职业背景。

1152
01:09:08,080 --> 01:09:09,680
okay? And...
好吧？然后……

1153
01:09:10,640 --> 01:09:13,200
I could have been, what, a lawyer, I think?
我本来可以是个律师，应该是吧？

1154
01:09:13,300 --> 01:09:14,880
A lawyer. A rich lawyer.
一个律师。一个富有的律师。

1155
01:09:15,180 --> 01:09:16,800
A professor, okay?
一名教授，行吗？

1156
01:09:16,920 --> 01:09:20,220
But instead, I'm teaching high school in China.
但我在中国教高中。

1157
01:09:20,820 --> 01:09:22,480
Right? Why am I doing this?
对吗？我为什么要这么做？

1158
01:09:23,700 --> 01:09:27,680
It's because... Um...
因为……呃……

1159
01:09:29,900 --> 01:09:31,220
I have three kids.
我有三个孩子。

1160
01:09:31,540 --> 01:09:33,620
Okay? I have three young kids.
好的？我有三个小孩子。

1161
01:09:34,760 --> 01:09:36,040
My eldest is six.
我的大儿子六岁。

1162
01:09:36,220 --> 01:09:37,960
My youngest is only about eight months.
我的小儿子才八个月。

1163
01:09:38,200 --> 01:09:40,760
Okay? And as a father,
我作为父亲，

1164
01:09:41,660 --> 01:09:45,220
you have to believe in a better world.
你要相信更好的世界。

1165
01:09:45,940 --> 01:09:49,520
But not only do you have to believe in a better world, you have to imagine.
但你不仅要相信更好的世界，还要去想象。

1166
01:09:49,840 --> 01:09:51,160
You have to fight for it.
你要为之而战。

1167
01:09:51,860 --> 01:09:53,820
Because... Um...
因为……呃……

1168
01:09:53,820 --> 01:09:58,500
You have to leave behind a legacy for your children.
你要为孩子们留下遗产。

1169
01:09:58,740 --> 01:10:00,460
Okay? So,
好的？所以，

1170
01:10:00,460 --> 01:10:06,120
why I teach this course is to bring you a message of hope.
我开这门课的原因是给你们送去一份希望的讯息。

1171
01:10:06,280 --> 01:10:08,760
Okay? Like, through your own imagination,
好吧？就是通过自己的想象，

1172
01:10:09,260 --> 01:10:12,400
through your own hard work, you can create a better world.
通过自己的努力，你们就能创造更好的世界。

1173
01:10:12,940 --> 01:10:15,620
You don't have to sit back and just let the world happen.
你不必坐着等着世界发生。

1174
01:10:16,100 --> 01:10:17,500
You don't have to wait for the future.
你不必等待未来。

1175
01:10:17,620 --> 01:10:20,060
You can make it happen. And...
你可以让它发生。并且……

1176
01:10:20,720 --> 01:10:22,620
If you really...
如果你真的……

1177
01:10:23,260 --> 01:10:27,580
work hard at it, you can make the world a better place.
努力去做，你就能让世界变得更好。

1178
01:10:27,800 --> 01:10:29,300
And I think, like, this year
我想，这一年……

1179
01:10:29,880 --> 01:10:31,340
has proven to me
已向我证明

1180
01:10:32,620 --> 01:10:34,920
that I can make the world a better place
我可以让世界变得更好

1181
01:10:35,820 --> 01:10:39,780
if I work hard. Because I've seen the growth in all of you.
只要我努力

1182
01:10:40,060 --> 01:10:43,720
Okay? So, I hope we can stay in touch.
好的？所以，我希望我们能保持联系。

1183
01:10:44,080 --> 01:10:45,580
I hope that...
我希望……

1184
01:10:46,060 --> 01:10:49,120
Um... You will tell me how you progress, because
嗯……你会告诉我你的进展。

1185
01:10:49,120 --> 01:10:52,600
I'm very confident that all of you will do very well in university.
我很有信心，你们在大学里会表现得很出色。

1186
01:10:52,620 --> 01:10:55,880
And in life. And maybe at some point,
在生活中也是如此。也许在某个时刻，

1187
01:10:56,640 --> 01:11:01,700
we can share this dream of psychohistory.
我们可以共享这份关于心理史的梦想。

1188
01:11:01,840 --> 01:11:06,340
You know? I know it sounds very complicated.
你知道吗？我知道听起来很复杂。

1189
01:11:06,580 --> 01:11:09,140
It's very abstract. But
很抽象。但

1190
01:11:09,140 --> 01:11:13,380
to make this work, you need a lot of people working together.
要把这件事做成，得有很多人一起合作。

1191
01:11:13,740 --> 01:11:16,060
Okay? And it's something that's not going to happen tomorrow.
好的？这件事不是明天就能完成的。

1192
01:11:16,280 --> 01:11:21,140
But it's something that we might come back to later on in our lives.
但它是我们以后生活中可能会再次回到的事。

1193
01:11:21,960 --> 01:11:23,800
Okay? So, that's it.
好的？好了，就是这样。

1194
01:11:24,200 --> 01:11:26,980
Thank you. And we'll stay in touch.
谢谢。我们会保持联系。

1195
01:11:27,020 --> 01:11:30,340
Okay? Subtitles by the Amara.org community
好的？字幕由Amara.org社区制作。
